ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of SHARON RUTH DUGGAN of Conception Bay South, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Dora Koop, whose term has expired.
